<TEXT>
<P>
NBC Makes Changes: "Amen" will rejoin NBC's prime-time lineup Saturday and two 
shows from the news division -- "Real Life With Jane Pauley" and "Expose" -- 
will replace the low-rated medical anthology "Lifestories" on Sunday night next 
month, the network announced Monday. "Amen" will air at 8 p.m. Saturday, 
replacing "Parenthood." 
</P>
<P>
