U.S. Reservists Called Up: 
</P>
<P>
Army: 69,000 
</P>
<P>
Marines: 10,800 
</P>
<P>
Navy: 4,500 
</P>
<P>
Air Force: 5,000 
</P>
<P>
Coast Guard: 1,000 
</P>
