COUNTY; BLACKS -- ORANGE COUNTY; RACIAL RELATIONS -- ORANGE COUNTY; RACIAL 
DISCRIMINATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA112790-0098 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 314082 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 27, 1990, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
