<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FarWest Financial -- A Nov. 24 story about FarWest Financial Corp. incorrectly 
stated the company's relationship with Michael Milken and Drexel Burnham 
Lambert Inc. FarWest and its subsidiary, FarWest Savings &amp; Loan, had only a 
remote business relationship with Milken, the former head of Drexel's junk bond 
division. Also, FarWest Savings purchased about $300 million of junk bonds from 
Drexel, not $600 million as was incorrectly reported. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
